## Home Page Component and CSS - Subheader/Subtitle

### JSX Component - HeroSection.tsx
**Location:** `/home/peterc/ccw/apps/frontend/src/pages/Home/sections/HeroSection.tsx`

```jsx
export function HeroSection({ title, subTitle }: HeroSectionProps) {
