```

The `subTitle` prop is passed from the parent Home component and rendered in a `<p>` tag with the `heroSubtitle` CSS class. The subheader text with emojis comes directly from Sanity's home document `subTitle` field.

### Parent Home Component - Home.tsx
**Location:** `/home/peterc/ccw/apps/frontend/src/pages/Home/Home.tsx`

The Home page component receives `homeData` from the loader and passes the `subTitle` to HeroSection:
```jsx
<HeroSection title={homeData.title} subTitle={homeData.subTitle} />
```

### CSS Styles - Home.css.ts
